  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Advanced Parkinson's disease for at least 5 years

          -  Good response to L-dopa

          -  Age 30 to 70 years

          -  Optimum oral therapy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Tremor only

          -  Dementia

          -  Very severe dyskinesia

          -  Previous brain surgery including deep brain stimulation

          -  Malignant disease
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
